#3018
guido lender~
Guido~
Guido, Merrick's cousin and partner, stands here flipping a coin.
~
Guido is smartly dressed in a grey tunic, tight silver trousers, and
a pair of highly polished black boots. He wears a heavy black cloak,
whose bright red silken lining shows briefly as he greets you and asks
you if you want to part with your gold. When you mention that just
maybe you want some of your deposits back, he scowls and tries to
talk you out of it, but finally reluctantly agreeing that if you
really want it (and asked just so) he would have to give it to you.
That admission gained, he seems to be trying to find a way to leave
without being seen, so if you want your money hurry up and ask now!
~
